{{!
    @template mod_scormremote/thirdlayer

    This is a template which will be contained multiple times in a wrapper. The wrapper must contain at least one index and can
    contain multiple.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * datasource - a url which target the href for a specific SCO content.
    * jssource - a url which target the src for a the javascript.
    * scormagainsource - a url which target the src for the scorm again api.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "datasource": "https://example.com/pluginfile.php/24/mod_scormremote/content/2/index.html",
        "jssource": "https://example.com/mod/scormremote/amd/src/layer3.js",
        "scormagainsource": "https://example.com/mod/scormremote/scorm-again/dist/scorm12.min.js"",
    }
}}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>Layer 3</title>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <script type="text/javascript" src="{{scormagainsource}}"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="{{jssource}}"></script>
  <style type="text/css">
    html,
    body,
    iframe {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    }

    #wrapper {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 100%;
    }

    iframe+#wrapper {
    display: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body onload="init();" data-source="{{datasource}}">
  <div id="wrapper">
    <h1>Your content is loading...</h1>
  </div>
</body>
</html>